Package: brownded
Title: Simulate bounded Brownian motion
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: c(person("Rory", "Nolan", email = "rorynoolan@gmail.com", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Sergi", "Padilla-Parra", email = "spadilla@well.ox.ac.uk",
                    role = c("ths")))
Description: Simulate bounded Brownian motion in any number of dimensions. 
    The particles are 'in a box' making elastic collisions with the walls. 
    Includes functionality for simulating images from diffusing fluorescent 
    particles.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
